# Does elevation change how a player performs?
# Similar players, abilities, check their elevation

library(httr)
library(jsonlite)
library(dplyr)

# Read the CSV file
cities <- read.csv("Resources/CityLatLong.csv")

# Create a function to get elevation
get_elevation <- function(lat, lon) {
  query <- paste0("https://api.open-elevation.com/api/v1/lookup?locations=", lat, ",", lon)
  res <- GET(query)
  data <- fromJSON(rawToChar(res$content))
  return(data$results$elevation)
}

# Add a new column 'elevation' to the dataframe
cities <- cities %>% 
  mutate(elevation = mapply(get_elevation, Lat, Long))
